message.content: a kitchen with dark grey cabinets and beige marble countertops; a white refrigerator to the right of the counter; on the counter, various items including a red jar of jam, a box of Jell-O, Alpen salt, a stack of plates, and a red canister; a sink with a silver faucet on the counter; a range hood above the sink; a wooden dining table with white chairs; on the table, various items including a bottle of water, a box of crackers, a mug, a glass, a knife, and lemons; the room has white walls and a brown parquet floor.
